Hivemind

Please Note That Not All Features (e.g. Music) Will Work In All Browsers. It is recommended, but not at all vital, that you use Google Chrome.




Instructions:

-Use A to move left
-Use D to move right
-Use W or SPACE to jump / fly (where appropriate)
-Click to launch use a special move (e.g. launch nanobots, swing sword, fire plasma cannon, etc.)
-Use Q and E to cycle through all players (e.g. converted robots / marauders)
-Click the restart button to restart (cyclic arrow)
-Click the pause button to pause (two lines)
-Get the astronaut to the end of the level to win
-Different enemies do different things when converted - use these abilities to your advantage


About the Game:

Hivemind is a puzzle platformer game made in 2021. It aims to fuse the puzzle-platformer and shooter genres to create an experience that will challenge your skill and your mind. You play as a scientist alone on a hijacked spaceship. Facing a vast robotic army, and insurmountable odds, you must use your inginuity and experimental technology to escape, by turning your enemies' strengths against them. As of February 2021, there are 30 levels - 3 chapters each with 10 sections.

Programmed By Will Punter in 2021
